title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 396: Featuring Mo Seider
description:
On this week’s episode of Spittin’ Chiclets, the guys are joined by Calder Trophy Winner Moritz Seider. Mo joined (01:29:46) to discuss his amazing rookie season with the Detroit Red Wings, meeting Stevie Y, growing up in Germany and tons more. The guys open the show discussing the Avs Cup Parade and the damage they are doing to the Cup. The boys also dive into the rumor mill, new coaches and tons more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
